replies.body:
This error has historically meant that there's an issue with your patcher reaching our patching servers properly. For this reason, I'd recommend going through the steps inside our [**connection guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues), as they're likely to resolve this issue for you.

Pls let me know how those steps went.
